\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid10360694 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Your present address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Bradfield, that's what the house is called, 28 Southlands Mount.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That's Riddlesden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, Riddlesden, Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You're a widow now, aren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The year when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  was...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 1919. Oh, no it wasn't. It were 1917. He was in the Army. It was 1919, I think, when we went to Bradford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The year when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 1887.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And the place where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Dauslack House, Utley, near Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Grandma lived there. We were away a wh
ile and then we were back again and when we left it I was working. I should be 14 or 15, then, when we left it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you left it the second time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. Well, it was never left. My grandma lived there and we moved somewhere else for a short time and then came back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 It was your grandmother's house, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me grandfather built it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And you and your parents moved somewhere else, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, near where me father was working for a short time, and then we came back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That was in Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it in the same district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, another district, Knowle Park district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Which of the houses would you life in longest as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I think the one at Utley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. I've a brother, that's Molly's father, and a sister that was killed in a motoring accident. I'm the eldest.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there just the 3 of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Just the 3, yes, and Molly's father's the youngest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I see. So there was you, then your sister, then your brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how much space would there be between the 3 of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, well, there was between me sister and I 2 years, and a lot more space between ... wait a minute. I'm 13 years older than John, so there'd be 11 years, wouldn't there, between my sister and John.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How old was your father when you were born, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When I was born? Oh, I don't know, I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, approximately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I couldn't say. Me father was killed in an accident, he was 56 when he was killed, in an accident at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I was working. John was 16 then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, well, that gives us an idea. Where did your father come from, did he come from Keighley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He came from Keighley, not Utley. Keighley, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He was a mill ... I think he was a mill mechanic, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was that in a spinning or weaving mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He didn't do that all the time. He used to work for an engineering firm in Keighle
y and go to the Exchange at Bradford at market days at one time, before he went to the mill at Bradford. But it was all to do with both spinning and weaving, all to do with that sort of machinery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was he a mechanic all the time, then, after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He was a mechanic all the time that he went to the Exchange, you see, he used to work the other days at the mill, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I see. He just spent one day on the Exchange and the rest of the week on the machinery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he have any other job at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
He wasn't a good scholar. I don't know how he managed going to an Exchange among business men, but he did. He left school when he was eight, eight years old, so he couldn't have had much schooling, could he. Still, he fought his way throu
gh with all these business people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he ever do any casual or part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember him ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or on strike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, he could always ... Bryn Smith's in Keighley, they wanted him once to take a job abroad for them, you see, he could always get work.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about your mother, do you know how old she would be when you were born? Was she about the same age as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 She wouldn't be over. I don't know, really. She wouldn't be young, she'd just be medium age, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would she be about the same age as your father, or possibly younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, there wouldn't be much difference in their ages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, in her young days they were all over
. Her father was a builder and he used to go about to places, he used to take cottages, and used to be blasting things, and all sorts. And they came from \{BLANK\} to Morton Banks, Keighley, the family, when she was young, and there was a family of 11.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Is that where she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Morton Banks? Yes, I think it would be, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Had she any jobs before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't really know what she did. I don't know what she did. She didn't work in a mill, I don't think. No, I couldn't say what she did.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think she did have a job, though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think she would, because most people had, hadn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she work at all after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, she never worked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I'd like to ask you about your life at home up 
to the time when you left school. This house, Dauslack House at Utley, do you know how many rooms there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
They were very big rooms. Very big rooms. One, two,....I don't know. Monster rooms; you could get 2 of this into one room. It was near a far
m, it was country, you know. There wasn't a big lot of rooms, but they were big. And an out-kitchen where they washed in a rain tub. You gathered water for washing in a rain tub, you know. And 2 big gardens, we had, but I'm not right sure how many rooms.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  and a kitchen downstairs or did you have more than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There were this big }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  that we seemed to be in most of the time and then another room like a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 sitting room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
, they used to call them then, didn't they. But it was a very ... very big rooms, not rooms like they are today.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was there a separate kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, for washing, it was an out-kitchen, you'd to go outside to it. It was a separate kitchen just for the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember at all how many bedrooms there'd be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No. Well, there was us there ... me brother wouldn't be born then, at that time, I don't think. We were all born at Dauslack House, all 3 of us. And there was use there, and Grandma, and Aunt there. Last part of ... when we w
ent back there me grandfather, he'd been killed in an accident off a bicycle. It's a right tragedy, me grandfather killed, Father killed in an accident, and me sister. The 3 generations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 All road accidents, were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, Father's was at work. T
hey were thawing something frozen up and throwing water onto it, and a young man was doing it and he says 'I'll finish it', and sent him away, and he fell onto a concrete floor as he were throwing, you see, and he never gained consciousness. Took him to B
radford Infirmary, and he died. So that was 3 generations, and 2 were road accidents, me sister and me grandfather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was the aunt your aunt who lived at the house? Was it your aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Mother's sister, she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 later on. She }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  late in life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did anyone help in the house, any servants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The washing, was that done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, in this outbuilding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They didn't make them. She used to mend things, yes. I don't think she made many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The clothes that you had, then, they would be bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would they always be new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, we always had new clothes. They always got us some nice things. She used to get us, me sister and I, b
etter things than she got herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 Was there any particular place that she went to buy for you?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't ... you see, a lot of the shops wouldn't be there now. I don't remember any particular place. Oh, yes, we used t
o have things made, that was when we moved from Dauslack House, there was a dressmaker at the end of the street and she used to make us things. We had a lot of things made by this dressmaker
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you were growing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, when we started work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But as a child your clothes would be bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They'd be bought, yes. But later on she made all we'd got. She was a good dressmaker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would it be shops in Keighley that your mother would buy the clothes from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, it would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have them at any particular time, you know, at any particular occasion? Or when did you have them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, you used to get them, didn't you Whitsuntide, and that, in days gone by, they usually had the most new clothes, didn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 For Sunday School and sermons and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we went to Sunday School. We went to Sunday school at Utley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about shoes, did your mother or father mend your shoes, at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think me father did a bit at one time. Yes, he did a bit. He didn't mend them all, but he'd patch them up and that, sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were they bought in Keighley, as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we got most of the things in Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How often would you have new shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. When they were done, I expect. We were never shabby, we were always kept nicely dressed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your father help your mother in the house with any of the jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, because you see there was ... same as when we were at Utley, and then when we moved again there was Grandma there. There was plenty 
to do, things without ... He used to be handy if anything had gone wrong, to mend it and that, you know. He was right handy in doing things like that but he didn't do any housework.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he do things like making the fire, or decorating? Repairs to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He'd do repairs. I don't think he decorated, I don't remember him decorating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he do any improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, he was very handy at doing anything that wanted doing, I mean the house that we went to after we left Utley, 
it was rented, and he never asked the landlady to do anything. He used to do anything that was to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he do anything for you as children, like dressing or undressing or bathing you, anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't remember that, either. If he did I've forgotten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He used to take me brother out, I can't remember us. We used to go to school and he'd been home at lunc
htime, he'd been home and we used to go to school, me sister at one side and me at the other, and we used to look up to him. And he'd be letting us go and he'd call us back and we'd get a halfpenny to join at. You could get a lot for a halfpenny, then. He
 used to give us a halfpenny to join at, many a time. Now, me brother, he used to take him }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4487535\charrsid1930154 every}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 Sunday from Utley to an aunt and uncle that lived in the village just above. He used to take him out always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he look after you while your mother went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, she didn't go out, they used to go out together. I don't think she went out on her own. You see, there was me grandma there all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she do much as far as looking after the children was concerned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Who?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Your grandma.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, she was all right. She was very good. She lived to be over 80.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Who actually ran the household, was it your grandma or your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me mother, mostly, and Grandma helped you see. And then this aunt, before she got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 , she helpe
d as well. 'Cos as I said, they were very big rooms and there wasn't ... we'd to carry water from the well, and we'd paraffin lamps, we hadn't gas or electric then. I think they have now, down there, but we hadn't when we were there. And sometimes}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4487535\charrsid1930154  the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  well dried up and we had to go into the village for water
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did that happen very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, just occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any tasks to carry out, you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we used to have animals. We had a goat, and rabbits, we used to look after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, the animals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, but was it you children who did the looking after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or did the parents look after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we looked after them. I looked after the goat mostly. Me sister used to tease it and
 it used to get its horns ready when it saw her coming (laughter).
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any jobs at all to do in the house, regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember any jobs. We might have done, but we didn't have any really work. When we got older ... yes, when we
 got older, when we were working, Grandma had died then, we used to do the ironing between us, me sister ... half it. I had to do half and she half, you see. The ironing. That was when we was older. Grandma had died when we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4487535\charrsid1930154 moved}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  from Utley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you, as the eldest child in the family, did you have to do anything for the younger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, no, I never had anything to do. Me sister and I used to be about together always, but I didn't have to do anything for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did the younger ones help to do anything for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What? At home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You didn't have to look after your younger sister or brother, say, at meal times, help to feed them or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, nothing like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have to go to bed at a certain time while you were going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. I couldn't tell you what time, but we didn't get to stay up late, not like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it your mother, or somebody else, who put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I expect when we were quite young it would be me mother. Then when we got older we put ourselves to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how old would you be, do you think, when you started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I don't know, but I don't remember being put to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So you'd really be quite young when you started doing it yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. You see, when there's 2 of you it's different to just one, isn't it. I think you do better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you share the bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What? We'd a bedroom, me sister and I together, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 This is what I meant.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We weren't with our parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you share a bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we had a bed. 'Course, there wasn't many twin beds in those days, was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would there possibly be 3 bedrooms, do you think?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, there would. There'd be 3 or 4.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Your parents would have a room, and ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Grandma would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And then what about when your younger brother came along, did he have a room to himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 only 2 when we left Utley. He doesn't remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What were the arrangements about bathing? There wouldn't, I presume, be a bathroom, would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. Of course, they had bath tins and that, then, don't they, big bath tins. I suppose we had that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where would that be, would it be ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There was a bath when we moved, after we left Utley, you see, there was a bath then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In the other house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But in this particular house ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you have a bath tin in the ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We should have a bath tin, I expect. I can't remember
, I don't remember it properly. 'Cos there wasn't hot water, you see, we should have to heat the water.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where would the water be heated, would it be in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ? Or out in this out kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 , I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So do you think you would have your bath in there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, not in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And you've no idea how often the bath tin would be got out when you were younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. I reckon we got bathed plenty, but I don't know how often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about stocks of new clothes, clean clothes, when you were a little girl? Would you have plenty of changes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, we'd plenty of changes. We were never short of clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where would you have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In this big }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would there ever be any occasion when you would eat somewhere else, say in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 sitting room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we might in ... we'd a summer house in the garden, we might in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That would be nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, with all the honeysuckle round it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where did your mother do the cooking? Was that in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 living room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of equipment had she, was it a range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. It was a big fireplace, that's all I know, and oven, so it'd be probably there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't suppose there'd be anything like a gas cooker, would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, there wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Can you remember anything about your meals and your mealtimes as a child? What was the procedure at breakfast time, when would you have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I can't remember that. I can't remember what we had. We always got plenty to eat, but I can't just remember what.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you all sit down to breakfast together, or would your father be off to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, Father would be off to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So there'd be your mother and your grandma and you and your sister, would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about lunchtime, or dinnertime, what did you call it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
We used to call it dinnertime. I don't remember what we had ... the usual things that they have, but I can't just remember what. I took agai
nst eating meat, I'm not a vegetarian because I eat fish and I have gravy. I get meat and ... I've been stewing some now and get good gravy out of it and I have that, but I never eat any meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you not as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, and she didn't bother, s
he thought, well, I would do. They all did but me, and she didn't bother to stress me. I don't eat bacon or ham or potted meat or meat, chicken, anything like that. And I've still stuck to it, and I haven't done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And your mother didn't mind at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, she thought I'd start when I got older, well, I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What was the attitude if you left anything uneaten on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember. They didn't force us to eat things if we didn't want them. I mean, they didn't force me to have m
eat, when I didn't just fancy it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Can you remember if you had any sort of special meals on Sundays or particular occasions?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We always used to have a Sunday dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 A joint and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And then teatime, would that be a light tea or a high tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We generally had something nice. You generally had something nice for your tea, especially on Sunday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would there be the sort of things like fruit and jelly or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And salmon or anything like that, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember there being tinned fruit or meat or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We had fruit in the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have anything before you went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We should have a light supper, I think. I can't remember that, either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about jam, or bottling fruit and things like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 She didn't do that, but she made her own bread and she made beautiful pasty, jam pasty. Everybody was taken with her jam pasty, rig
ht thin and ... oh, it was lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she make pickles or wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 She didn't like pickles. She didn't like onions and pickles and that. I do, but she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about wine, did she make any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or any medicines, had she any recipes for making medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No herbal mixtures, or anything like that?
