No, she didn't make any jam. We'd blackcurrants and gooseberries in the garden and that, but I don't think she made any jam. She wasn't really fond of jam, I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was any beer brewed for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
