\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, she hadn't enough, because we'd a lot of flowers in the garden, see, a lot of room taken up with flowers.
