\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You've mentioned your livestock that you kept, your goat and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Rabbits.
