He wasn't a big eater, no. He wasn't a big eater. We always had a lot of fruit. Oranges, he used to bring a lot home, buy a lot, you know. frui
t. to eat raw. We always had a lot, all my life we had. I still eat a lot of fruit. The specialist - I had a cataract taken off one eye - and he said I couldn't do better than eat an orange a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you allowed to talk during the mealtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you, in fact, talk a lot at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't think we'd talk a lot, else we couldn't've eaten, could we (laughter), not if we talked too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you choose what you wanted from what was cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, it was brought to you, but you always liked it. You never got anything that you didn't want.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
If there was something that you wanted, like the salt, could you ask for it to be passed to you or did you have to wait for it to be offered round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh you could ask, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And could you ask for a second helping of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, if you wanted one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you taught to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember being taught. I don't know, it seemed to come to you, didn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they expect you to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4487535\charrsid1930154 sit}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  in a certain way at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we were never pulled up a lot about ... you know, we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 always seemed}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  to behave ourselves, I think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you bring toys to the table, or a book?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we didn't do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what about leaving the table, when could you leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We couldn't leave unless we asked to leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you normally have to wait until everybody had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, no, if you asked you could leave, you see, you were given permission to leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you all sit at the table for your meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have the same places regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, the same places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it your mother who served up, or did your father ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Mother. Mother mostly. Father wasn't a good one for carving, or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother do the carving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Mother did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What order were you served it? Was there a special order, or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember that, I don't think there were any special ... no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember where your younger sister, or possibly your brother, sat before he was old enough to feed himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't remember. I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You don't remember whether there was a high chair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think he would have, but I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of person was your mother? Was she easy to talk to, did you feel close to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, she was a good mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel that you could confide in her if you had any ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, you could confide in her
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she show her affection particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, she wasn't too fussy with you, but you know that it was there, the affection.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Father was the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel that you could confide any worries in him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. 'Course, he was only 56 when he was killed, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I meant as a child did you feel ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You see, I wouldn't be very old then. Well, I was working, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we always behaved respectfully towards them, always. We'd a happy childhood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they bring you up to behave towards your brother and sister in a particular way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we all got on together, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they say if you should hit back, or not, if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't ... they didn't teach you to be fighting, I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they teach you to stick up for yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What kind of people do you think they hoped you'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 grew}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they hoped you'd be respectable, g
ood-living people. That's all they could hope for, isn't it. And we all turned out all right, as it happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they bring you up to consider that certain things were important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't remember anything special, you know, any special thing that they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What did they think about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we never heard anything like that. Me father was never one that used bad language.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When the grownups were talking could you children join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I expect so. 'Course, I don't think they joined in then as much as they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But were you allowed to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I think, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 If you did something that your parents disapproved of, what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You'd get punished for it, I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Can you remember ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I can't remember ... I don't remember what I'd done, I remember Mother gave me a thump on the back and it set me nose }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
