me back and it stopped eventually. Oh, yes, we had to behave ourselves. I'd done something wrong then, I don't know what now, but she gave me a thum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4487535\charrsid1930154 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  on me back and me nose started bleeding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what was the reaction to that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, she was upset, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you punished in any other way, you know, not necessarily physically?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you chastised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, never made to do anything for punishment, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you say that your mother or your father would carry out a
ny punishment more so than the other? If it had to be done, would it be your mother or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. I think they'd both be alike if we'd to be punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think that you received the ideas you had about how to behave equally from both your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or more from one than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I think from both of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you had a birthday would that be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We had a party, and you see, as I said, they were big rooms and there was a piano. Yes, we got a birthday party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would there be children invited?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Children and cousins, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They used to bring little birthday presents, and we used to be dancing about, but unfortunately I coul
d play the piano a bit and I'd always to play, I couldn't join in (laughter).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you all have a birthday party when it was your birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me sister and I did, you see, me brother was too young and I don't know whether he had them or not the same as us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Can you remember how you used to spend Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. We were just all there together, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You'd have a Christmas ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We'd have a Christmas tree, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about a Christmas dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me father use
d to get a goose given from where he worked, I think. There used to be somebody come for the dinner, a young man that used to work with him, I think, sometimes for Christmas dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You didn't have any other guests, members of the family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or friends, or anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And you played the piano, did anybody else play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No. Me brother had some lessons and he never made anything out. I can't play now. We had a pianola at Bradford, but we gave it away, it was too big, we couldn't bring it here, so I've lost all I knew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any other musical instruments as well as the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, just the piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did anybody sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not ... you know, they'd all sing together, but no one special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you in the habit of having a sort of musical get-together, a singsong sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, just occasionally, yes, when it was anything special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they used to do at the parties, you know, they'd join in. when we had the parties.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they at any other time, do you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They didn't at any other time. We used to play a lot out of doors there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember at that stage when you were a child, whether there were books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. We got prizes from Sunday School. I've a lot of them now, upstairs, prizes I got when I went to Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about newspapers or magazines, did you have those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know what we got because we didn't read them then, not when we were young. They would get newspapers, but I couldn't just say.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember your mother and father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, me father wasn't a big reader. As I say, he hadn't had much schooling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could he read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, he could read a bit, yes,
 but he hadn't had a lot of schooling. Yes, he could read, a bit. I tell you, he left when he was 8, he couldn't've had much. He'd learnt himself, what he did. Mother was ... I think she was a good scholar at school
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents ever read aloud, either to you children or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't remember that. They might have done, but I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember there being a funeral in the family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I remember me grandfather's when he was killed at Leeds on his bicycl
e. I remember that, them bringing it down the lane, the coffin, for the funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Who would attend the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, me mother ... there were still some of her brothers and sisters, you know, all those. Although some of them had gone to America.
 One sister next to me mother had gone to America, and somebody else had, but still there were still some of the family left that attended the funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you children go, or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember going to the funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What was the convention about mourning clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, they used to wear black, you know. You know those capes they used to have, well she had one of those, a right nice cape. They made them look ... capes and bonnets, didn't they, they made them look old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long did she wear that after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, she used to wear the cape normally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Always?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. They used to wear these capes and bonnets, they didn't dress as young as they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, but I mean the special mourning one, how long would she ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, there wasn't a special mourning one, she didn't any special mourning, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long did people stay in mourning after a funeral, after a death?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Quite a lot longer than it is now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, they don't get any black now, do they, much. They used to stay many a time a year, didn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you taken out to visit neighbours or friends or relatives when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, only people that were just two more houses near and they used to come up, and that's al
l. I don't remember being taken out visiting much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about shopping, were you taken out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, we used to go. As we got a bit older we could do the shopping when we lived at Utley. We'd a bit distance to walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it your mother who took you shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you ever go out with just your father, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't ... me brother, he used to take him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember any special outings with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. The first holida
y that we had, I was about 12, and it was 4 days to Blackpool. That was the first time we had a holiday altogether. They didn't go off like they do today, did they, and it was just 4 days. We thought it was wonderful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, played about on the beach, I think, mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents play with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They sat on the beach, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Holidays after that, did you have them more frequently? Was that the start of a series?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That was the start. We used to get for a week later on. We went with our parents always. for our holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Until you were quite grown up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Even when we were grown up. When we'd young men they went and stayed in another house. I know me sister's and mine, they were both our husbands later, they went with us, you see, and we were with our parents. Then we didn't go separate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you do anything special on Bank holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, nothing special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you spend your Saturdays as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I don't know. I know me Saturdays when I got working I used to help a lot in the sweet shop, later, when I got working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But as a child what would it be, would you be playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We'd be playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you go shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We'd be playing out, yes, I don't know. She should be with our parents if we went shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We went to Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have different clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We had Sunday clothes, yes, that we didn't wear other times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you play games on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. I don't think we did, but I don't know that we were barred from it. I don't think we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you know whether your parents thought that it was wrong to work or play on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't think so, no, I don't think they thought so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they attend a place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In their young days ... they were Church of England, really, both of them, but in their young days before they was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  they both attended the Salvation Army, although they belonged to the Church of England, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they belong to the Salvation Army within your memory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, that was before they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 , and I think they'd get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  when they were going there. I don't think they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 at the Salvation Army, I don't know. I think it would be Keighley Parish Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 From the time that you can remember did they go to Church fairly regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, they didn't go a right lot, no. We went to Sunday School, we were sent off always. We had to attend Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any social outings or any social activities connected with the Sunday School you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 As we were older we used to have rambles. Yes, we used to go on those when we got older, you see, belonging to the Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 As a small child did you have a Sunday School treat or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I can't remember any treats, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember any other social activities organised by the Church at all that you took part in? Any clubs, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. I used to teach a class of young boys, the first class at Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how old }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 would}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  you be then, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That'd be in me 'teens, then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I were in the choir, both me sister and I. It were only a small church at Utley. We were both in the choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 From being quite small, were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, we should be in our 'teens, I think. Yes, I have a present, a wedding present, a barometer in there that the choir gave when we were }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did the Church have a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was Grace said at meals in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we said our prayers at night, yes, before we went to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have family prayers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we didn't have family prayers, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you know if your father took any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, he didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, I knew. He was a Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Have you any idea why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about your mother was she interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. She was the same, I think. But they weren't interested, you know, not to take a leading part in them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember your mother or your father voting in a general election before 1919? 1918 was the first election that women could vote at.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they would vote, but I can't ... I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would it be the Conservative Party that they'd vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They were always}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154  Conservatives}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In some places at that time people felt that they risked losing 
their job or their house if they voted differently from their employer, did that apply at all in the case of your father, do you think, or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't think so. When ... I know when I was a work when it was voting time we always used to all wear our
 different coloured rosettes on at work, really more for fun than anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you as a child have rosettes at election time, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, you see, I was working then, I should be in me 'teens. I didn't have when I was younger, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember your father or your mother ever doing anything for the Conservative Party at election time, or at any other time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, they weren't so keen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When your parents weren't actually doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they stayed at home, and as I say, at Utley there were a big garden and plenty to do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your father take a big interest in the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not a big interest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, me mother did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother have any interest outside the home and the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, she hadn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not on her own, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 If she did go out, who would she go with?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What time, about, would he get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, he worked ... See, when he worked in Keighley he'd be home sooner, about half past 5 or 6, and a bit later when he worked at Bradford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, all of them, he never went out. He never went out on the evenings on his own. He'd spend the time at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he ever attend a club, or go to a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 She didn't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your father take part in any sport, at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, he wasn't sporty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he ever go to the races, or have a bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't think so. I don't remember him...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, for sickness or funeral or insurance, anything of that sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, she paid in for us in that lit
tle brief, a penny a week. I kept it up because I thought it was a shame not to when your parents had got it and now, when I've got to this age, you see, I don't have to pay anything. It isn't much you get, but still, I didn't feel like letting it slide w
h
en they'd paid it. And she always used to give us... it wasn't much a week, and we used to take it to the Penny Bank, you know, we had a little banking account each, and that had to be saved. Sometimes it was only a penny or twopence and it had to go ther
e.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
The Penny Bank. Yorkshire Penny Bank. It's called the Yorkshire Bank now. And it was surprising when we got into our 'teens how that had mounted up, with just that little bit.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you get on with your brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, we got on well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel particularly close to one of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, I was very close to me sister with being of an age, you see. Me brother, he lives just below Molly's father, he comes up every morning, I expect to see if I'm all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 As a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me sister, and cousins used to come and play, with having plenty of room. There was fields, and that, where we lived. Cousins used to come.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there any neighbours' children around that you played with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No, there wasn't any. Oh, yes, there was, from a farm. Rose, Cottage, yes, we used to go up there and play at this farm. And I think she's living yet is the girl that we used to play with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, particular game, I don't think, just play about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you play any street games or ball games, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we just used to play about. When we were in the field we did. Of course it was a street after we'd moved, you know. We used to play i
n the street then with other children. I don't know what we played, though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What happened if you got dirty while you were playing? What would your Mother say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember her being cross with us at all. I don't remember us getting right dirty, though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you play with anybody that you chose, or were there children that your parents would discourage you from playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. There wasn't any children at Utley and we could play with anyone we chose when we were at the other place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you belong to any youth organisations at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, no. Primrose League I was in, that's all. That was at the Church, wasn't it. Yes, it was, wasn't it, when I went to the Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any particular hobbies, apart from keeping your pets did you collect anything, or do gardening
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I hadn't any particular hobbies, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you go fishing, or go for walks, or bicycling at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we didn't fish. We used to walk, go for walks about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 With whom?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well someti
mes... sometimes we'd go mushrooming, something like that, with our mother, you know, in the fields, 'cos there was mushrooms about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was there any poaching done in those parts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't remember any poaching. 'Cos there wasn't any game, or anything, there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. I was never sporty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you ever go to a theatre or a concert or music halls? Cinema, Anything of that sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We used to go only to a pantomime now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how old would you be when you would go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I should be in me 'teens then, 15 or 16.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You say that you got a bit of pocket money that you put in the bank.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we didn't touch that, Mother gave that to go in the bank and then we got money to spend as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How much did you get?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
I don't know, now. And if we got any money when it had been birthdays, I remember we used to go into Keighley and get ... you could get a quarter 1b. box of Fry's chocolate creams for threepence half-penny, then, we us
ed to buy them with money that we got when it had been birthdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you get a regular amount from your parents, apart from these odd half-pennies that your father gave you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we used to get something at Saturday but I don't just know how much. It wouldn't be a big lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And it would be sweets or chocolates that you bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, that we bought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did anyone outside the home help your mother to look after the house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There was your grandma there, wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 If your mother was ill or confined to bed, how did she manage? Did your grandma take over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember her being ill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember what happened when, say, your young brother was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, of course, we were ol
der then, I was ... Oh, no, I wouldn't be working. Yes, I was. I can't remember what happened then, but Grandma was there, you see. He was born at Dauslack House. We all were.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents have any other relatives living }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 nearby}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, only th
is aunt and uncle up in the village where he used to take me brother when he was a bit older, you know, on Sunday, always up. Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And was that as much as you saw of them? Or did they visit your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, occasionally they used to come down, not a lot because they had a shop, see, they hadn't a lot of time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents have friends there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. Not a lot of friends. No, they hadn't a lot of friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But they had some?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Some, but not many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 Where}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  did they see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, at home, that's all. I don't know of anywhere else. They all seemed to come home, with it being nice we used to have a lot of visitors there, you know, with it being nice and country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents visit their friends' homes as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it all one way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 All one way, 'cos people liked coming there, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother and father share their friends, or did your father have his own and your mother have her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, the same friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were these friends actually invited to come to the house or did they just come...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They used to come just as they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were they offered anything to eat and drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They'd be offered their tea, I think, when they come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And they would call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Without an invitation, yes, most of them
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about neighbours, would they ever come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There wasn't any ... there was only 2 houses lower down, there wasn't any neighbours, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But the people from those houses, did they visit you at all or did you visit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we were friendly with them but I don't think they visited each other's houses much.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When the friends came would they come for particular occasions as well as coming casually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, they just came casually, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would they come at birthdays, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, no, at birthdays we had children, you see, always for us, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But if it was your mother or father's birthday, for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They didn't have anything, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 People say that in those days they used to make their own amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What do you think your parents did with their friends when they got together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they used to play the piano, and sing, and singsong, and that. That's about all that was done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they play any games, card games or anything of that sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we never had any card games, much, no. They weren't keen on cards, I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Many people divide society into
 different social classes, social groups; in the time before 1918 did you think of people belonging to one social class and others to a different one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, sometimes you used to think some people weren't quite as good as you, didn't you. At times, certain people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there some particular people that you know that ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154 one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 class}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160489\charrsid1930154  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
on the whole, you know. There were not many people. Most people you knew they were more like yourself. Most of the people we knew were more like ourselves. We didn't think they were lower than us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
If you had to divide society into different classes at that time, what would you say the different classes were? I mean, how many for instance? Would you say there were two classes or 3 classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know. Just some people didn't seem to bother, you see, to keep themselves tidy, and that. That's what I was meaning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I can't. But me fathe
r would have given, if anybody had asked him, he'd have given his last penny. He was that type, if anyone had asked him for it, this penny, he'd have given it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you ever taught to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 curtsey}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  or show any special respect to any particular person or group of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember anybody showing respect to your parents in any particular way?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Calling people 'sir' or 'madam' or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, they were respected but I don't remember any particular ... you know, way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Who were considered the most important people in the district where you lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, now, I don't know. There were a lot of good people in those days. A lot of ... Same as on the Council, and the mayors, and t
hat, there seemed to be a different type to what they are today, a lot of them, but I can't single any particular one out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you mean that they were probably more refined or something like that, or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They were respected, whole families in the town, a lot of them, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would they be fairly well-off families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they'd be better off than most people, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would they be representative of any particular type of people, employers, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they did employ people as well, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there many employers living around in Keighley at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, a few. Sir Robert Clough and people like him, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of people were they and who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I didn't know them personally, I only knew them by name, only they were all respected.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about shopkeepers, for instance, how did they rank?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The shopkeepers were more polite than they are today. Well, shop assistants aren't, they don't seem to care 
whether you take it or leave it, today. Then you tried to oblige people. We always did. Although we were fortunate with assistants we had, we were very fortunate. Some good girls, which we got from the Telegraph, just adverts, all of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was this in Bradford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Yes, one of them comes to see me every month and she does some cleaning up while she's here. And another one, she makes a cake every Christmas for me, and me birthday, and she was an assistant. And she also made us a Golden Wedding cake. A
nd you know, they tried to sell things, then, they tried to sell things to people, but today ... And a lot of them can't reckon up. I'm 83 and I can reckon up a lot better than a lot of them now because I kept it up, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But the shop keepers themselves, as opposed to the shop assistants, in those days what sort of people would they mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, I know by the people at Bradford that were there, well, they were all very nice people. There was a block of shops where we were and they were all nice people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about in Keighley before you went to Bradford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I don't know, you see, I don't know the shopkeepers in Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about the clergy, what sort of people did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 Utley}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  Church we had
 some nice clergy. One of them, he used to take the choir boys to the pictures. He's dead now, I think. He was a curate at the Church. Me brother was one of them, he was a choir boy, he used to get taken. And when it was our Golden Wedding, I was surprise
d, I got a card and he'd been a boy in my class at Sunday School at Utley, sent me a card. He saw it in the paper and sent a card. He was, like, the same age as me brother, he was in the Sunday School class when he was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what sort of family did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Who? This boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, I didn't know his family, I only knew him. Only I thought, well, he's been nicely brought up when he thinks to send a card, hasn't he, so long after. And he's never seen me, I wouldn't know him if I saw him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What were the teachers like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Teachers at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, they were good. And to my idea they were far before a lot of the teachers today. I don't think they know as much as they did in that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think they seemed a different type of person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Different type of person, and I think they ought to teach the children today something that'll be useful for them in after life instead of all these things that's no good to them. They have all sorts of subjects that's no use at all to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What were the teachers like as people outside the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 They were good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In the community at large, you know, did they take much part in the life of the community? Who did they seem to knock around with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well I don't
 know much about them outside school. But the headmaster at Utley, he was keen on singing and that, and he always had them singing things out of musical comedies (laughter), which was quite a change, wasn't it. You know, and they got interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was this out of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, in school, the singing lesson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about farmers? There would be farmers around, I suppose, would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, there was a farmer's man in that farm by us which was .... he was always very nice and helpful.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they have much social life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would they be working most of the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
They'd be working, yes, 'cos there was just him, you see. And people used to get drowned in the River Aire, drown themselves, commit suicide, and he used to have to fetch them up in the farm cart. The River Aire was just below.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was this a sort of regular thing that he was asked to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 If anyone drowned themselves they always asked him. to take the cart down, which wasn't very nice. 'Course, they h
ad to get them away somehow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of people would you say went to the church that you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, a lot of nice people. A lot of nice people from that church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there any other churches near, chapels, you know...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There was a cha
pel, but I think that closed. Now, the church is still there, because when my husband died I took him ... I had him taken in, we went in there, in the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But the chapel was going in the days when you lived there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, it was Congregational. Oh, and there's another, there's a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 Wesleyan}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 Chapel still going not far away. But the Congregational has closed, and it was a nice chapel. I went to Sunday School a bit there at the Congregational and that aunt that lived with us was teaching there I went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So did you go to 2 Sunday Schools, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I went to that Congregational first and then to the church, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you notice any difference between the sort of people who went to the church and the people who went to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, no, they were all very nice people in both places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 One lot wouldn't be, say, a wealthier lot than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think there'd be more that were wealthier at the church 'cos there were a few families that went to church that was fairly well off.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you say that people similar to yourself would all have the same standard of living in that area, or would there be different groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 There'd be some that were poorer, poorer than we were in that area, and some that were wealthier.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you know any particular family that you could describe that was, say, a poorer family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. In the low part of Utley there were some poor houses, you see, poor places, and a lot lived there which I didn't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Have you any idea what sort of people they would be, what sort of jobs the men would do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't know. They never seemed to do anything wrong, but they were just poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were some families thought of as 'rough' and others as 'respectable'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, there were always some that were thought rough, wasn't there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was there any one that you knew about, any particular family that you knew about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, you were thought rough on the whole if you ... No, I don't know of any particular family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think that any group felt itself superior to any other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
I think they do that more today than they did then, all trying to outdo one another. Want to be at the top. I don't think they did as much then, wanting to outdo one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember a distinction between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, they did. They never looked down on anybody. As I say, me father would have given his last penny to anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class, or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I don't think she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You say that she was better educated than your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, she didn't go to a better school or anything, but y
ou see, she went to school longer and got on better. But she used to go to Riddlesden School, up here, the church school, up here, when they lived in Morton Banks. And she was a better scholar than he was. Well, she'd had the schooling, you see, which he 
hadn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think this difference had any effect at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, no, he always got through.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But her family didn't feel that she was marrying somebody ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. Well, I don't suppose they'd know. And he always didn't do bad at work, you see, he got on at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was it possible in those days for somebody to move from one class of society to another? You know, to move up in the world?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Or down in the world?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember anybody being described as 'a real gentleman' or 'a real lady'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, yes, there were lots of people. I don't just remember their names, now. Lots in Keighley that did a lot of good. And that's what I call a real gentleman, when they've done a lot of good, don't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of people would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, they were people that were fairly wealthy, that they did a lot of good with what they had. Nowadays they don't get enough, they're grabbing all they can. most of them, and then they haven't enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No, not at all. We'd to go down a lane to it but we never went, if we'd been anywhere me father met us, we never went down in the dark, not along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where would the nearest police be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Just up in the village, I should think. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Have you any idea what their relationship was with the community? How did people feel about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they never seemed to be needed, not where we were, anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You say that your second house was rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Your first house, was that owned by the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, that was rented. Me grandfather built it and it didn't sell and then he rented it, you see. The people didn't sell it that h
e built it for, and then he rented it, that first one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I see. Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we did of the second one, a landlady it was. Yes, she lived just across.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 This was the landlady of the other house, of the second house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What about the first house, did you see anything of that...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, we did, yes. Yes, we saw them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you feel about them as landlords?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, they were both all right, both of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember feeling ever that your parents were having a struggle to make ends meet?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You were never short?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We were never short.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you given lessons at all by anybody before you actually started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think I should be 5, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What were the school hours when you first started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you go all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I went all day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 It would probably be something similar to what it is today?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Similar to what it is today, I think, yes, it would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of a school was it that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, it was what they called Board schools, then, didn't they. I never went to a better school. The one at Utley was a Board school, as well. I didn't go to any better school, ever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you just attend one school throughout your school life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I went to Holy Croft, that's the time we was away from Utley, and Utley, that's all. Just those two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Which one did you go to first, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Holy Croft.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And it would be a day school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you get there? How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not long from where we lived, only 5 minutes, perhaps, from where we lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Walk, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did anybody go with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think mother would take me. I've forgotten, but I think she'd take me, then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have your midday meal at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, at home. There wasn't school meals, then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I liked school, yes. I always got on well at school
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you feel about the teaching and the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I always liked the teachers and I liked school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they emphasise things as being important, things like manners, tidiness, or being punctual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No. At Holy Croft I got a doll from the teacher, I didn't know I was getting it, for being the best girl in the class. She dressed it, and I was surprised when I got it. I had it until a few years ago. Me father got a glass case for me to p
ut it on, and I gave it to someone only a few years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How old would you be when you got that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, about, perhaps, 7. Or eight. No older I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were they bothered about the way you spoke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And what about if children were late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't remember anyone being late, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 If you did something that the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know, 'cos I don't think I ever did anything. I wasn't punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you remember anybody else being...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, no, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Wasn't anybody ever kept in or made to stand in a corner or something of that sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they may have been but I don't remember in a corner. I can't remember anything, really, about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents show an interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, they were interested, you could tell when you got the cupboard for me doll.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they meet your teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, the teacher .... had to ask the teacher to come home when it had got under this glass, you know. She came on to her tea, I think.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But I mean regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Hadn't met her before, just to let her see the doll.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents ask what you had been doing at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did they ever visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. I don't think they visited then like they do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did the other children come from similar types of home to yours, or from different types?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, most of them there, that first school I went to, were from differen
t ... the same kind of homes as I came from, you see, the same kind of houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I never noticed any favouritism, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did any of the children seem to be left out of things at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, they didn't seem to be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Then you went on from Holy Croft to the school at Utley when you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, when we moved back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And how was that? You would still go home for your dinner, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, it'd take about ... a bit longer but not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you go on your own then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, me sister was there, you see, there were two of us. That's what I say, you see, when we were coming up 
with me father, when we got the halfpenny to join at.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you like that school compared to the ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I liked Utley school best.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, it was a smaller school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was that why you liked it better?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think so, 'cos it was smaller, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were the teachers similar?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Yes, the teachers were similar. The teachers were as good at Holy Croft, but it was just because it was a smaller school I liked it better. The teachers were as good at both places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And was the atmosphere at the school similar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How old were you when you left that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think I'd be 15. Then I started work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you have stayed longer if you could have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, I'd got as high as I could get at that school. I was there months when I really wasn't learning anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So you really felt you were wasting your time the last part you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you attend any part time classes at all after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I never went to any night school or anything after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, at one time I was wanting to be a teacher, but I had a bit of trouble with me head, bad pains, and that, and it was given up, the idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 While you were still at school did you have a part time job as a means of earning a little money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When was it that you started helping in the sweet shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, that was later, but I went to work, you see.
 When I went to work I went to a sweet manufacturing place, you see, chocolate dipping when I went to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That was when you were 15?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you get the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Me father went with me, (laughter) They go }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 their selves}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  today, don't 
they? And I got it, and I didn't work anywhere else, and I finished up in the Keighley office - no, in the Bradford office. Keighley office I worked ... after I'd worked in the factory, but to box make and lucky bag make and all sorts of things, then I fi
n
ished up in the office and I didn't know anything about office work and I said to Mother 'they won't keep me long, I'll be out in a fortnight'. Anyhow, I did, I managed. And then, after Keighley office I was moved down to the warehousing office down at Br
a
dford and I was moved there, to Bradford. And all I was going for was 3 months and they never mentioned ... I didn't like it at first, then I got to like it and I used to go on the 7.15 train from Keighley in the morning to Bradford. And I got to like it 
and they didn't mention me coming back, and I didn't, so I stayed there until I left. And that's how we got the shop at Bradford, one of the travelers got it. And at the Bradford office I used to take the money from 6 travellers and keep the books.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I 
wonder if we can get some dates, some periods, for the various jobs that you did. In 1902 you went into the factory doing the chocolate dipping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And you say it was piece work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, a halfpenny a lb.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What exactly did you have to do? You were just dipping chocolates into..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
You worked at a slab, you did them with your fingers and put them on a tray. And even the small chocolate creams you only got a halfpenny a lb., and some big chocolate chips you still got a halfpenny a lb. for them, you liked them 'cos you soon got a lb.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
I don't know, it was about .... Oh, I know at the latter part, I don't know... I think we started about 7. Yes, I think so. But I know at the latter part, those hours at K
eighley, I had the keys for the sugar boilers and all the lot to get in and we had to be there for 7 to let them get in, so I think I must have started, when we started early, at 7.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What time did you finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I think it was 5 or 6 o'clock, it would be. Six o'clock, I fancy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What sort of a lunch }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 meal break}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 An hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you just have the one break in the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You didn't have a breakfast break, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was this Monday to Saturday or Monday to Friday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Monday to Saturday, Saturday morning, yes, not all day Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You finished at dinner time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any holidays from your work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Just the ordinary holidays, you know. When it was Keighley holidays, and that, we had a holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were you paid at all for that, or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 The money that you earned, the piecework rate, did you feel that that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, it was then, you know, because money went a lot further. I mean for a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12135312 \'a3}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  you could get a lot of things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you give the money intact to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And did she give some of it back to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 She gave me some spending money, I don't know what, now, I've forgotten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was your wage put into the family budget or was it put into anything special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 It was put into the ... for us to live off, I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you get on with the other people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 All right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did your employer treat you? How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You didn't see much of them, you know, not 'till you'd got later on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But did you feel that he was a good employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you feel about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I enjoyed the work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Actually doing the chocolates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long would you stay doing that sort of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
I don't know how I managed to get into the office, I went ... Should stay a few years. A few years, I don't just know how much. And then later I got into the office and d
id the office work. As I told you, I was always a good scholar, and I picked it up and I could do the ledgers, and that. I soon picked it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Didn't you do something else before you actually went into the office, though? You said making up lucky bags and things like this.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, I did all those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you call that a sort of packing job, really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Making wood boxes, and general things, all sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What other things would you do in the course of your work? Before you went into the office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Well, if the bottle-washer hadn't turned up sometimes you had to go down and wash the bottles (laughter). You know, you had to give your had to anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Can you remember whether you were still doing that sort of work, or whether you'd gone on into the office job by 1911?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, I should be in the office then, because I was a few years at Bradford, you see, and I left in ... I went to the shop in 1919. 1919 to the shop that we had, Bradford Newsagents and Tobacco. And my husband gave h
is job up, you see, and I had him to train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 So there'd be 9 years between...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Between Keighley and Bradford office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Between your actually starting work and 1911, and then there'd be 8 years between then and your actually having your own business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And you think you would spend more time in the office part, prior to that, than you did in the manufacturing side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I did. 'Cos I was a few years in Keighley Office, then a few years in Bradford office, you see. And a girl 
that worked with me in Bradford office, she came as a junior - she was up here the other week for tea, she never got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
. So I always got on very well with the people that I worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And since 1919 you've had your own business until you retired, have you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we were 32 years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And this was a sweet shop and tobacco ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Newsagents, sweets and tobacco. I worked at the Bradford office on the Saturday and gave me keys up, all me keys up, and went into the shop of our own on the Mo
nday, so I'd no holiday. And then it was hard work, a struggle when you're starting on your own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you have preferred any other type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't think so, I enjoyed ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You mentioned teaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, well, I'd given that 
up because me head was bad, but I enjoyed all the time we were at Bradford, every minute of it, although it was hard work because then we were open 'till 9. We were open early for newspapers, you know, 6 o'clock, and had the shop open 'till 9, and 10 at S
aturday. And we had some help, but we never kept them all that time, we did it ourselves. And we did holidays ourselves. We did good at holidays. But we always managed ourselves and let them have a holiday, the girl that we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you serve any apprenticeship or training in connection with your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No. I didn't with bookkeeping, and I had to take from 6 travellers, cash, and keep the cash book, and I never had any bookkeeping training at all, I picked it all up meself.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you belong to any trade union or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Newsagents' Association, and the tobacco we did, in Bradford, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But before that, when you were an employee of the firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you take any part in the activities of the Newsagents' Association?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, not in the Association, we didn't. We'd perhaps go to a dance or something like that, but that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests, the same outlook, or different? Towards the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What? Employees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Employers and employees, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we were very fortunate, we had some good ones. We hadn't a bad one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 In your time as an employee, previously, did you feel that them employees and the employer had the same outlook then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, they were very good to me, was my employer, yes. They were helpful when we went to the shop, as well, and some of the directors were.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest amongst the workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, there didn't seem to be divisions amongst the workers like there is today, I'm sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you feel that there was a big division between trained craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I don't know, but today they're never satisfied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Would you say that starting full time work changed your general attitude to life, at all? in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. No, I took an interest in me work whatever I was doing. I was interested in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Then you had this part time job in a sweet shop, didn't you. When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That's since we came up here. It was a friend that had the sweet shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I see, that's fairly recent, is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I can't do it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I'm sorry, I thought it was some time earlier.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 After we got up here a friend had a sweet shop in Keighley and asked me to go help them a
t Christmas, you see, when they were busy, which I right enjoyed doing, but I could see then and I can't see right, now. And then when they were stocktaking she asked me to help with that, 'cos I'd done a lot of stocktaking. I'd done a lot of stocktaking 
i
n the firm I worked for had 3 shops at one time, and 2 warehouses, and I'd done a lot of stocktaking and pricing up with that, you see. And so she asked me if I'd help them to take stock and price it in. And then when they were selling out she asked me if
 
I'd do it again. Now, the person that was taking it, she got me to go and help them at busy times, the person that took it, you see. Then I had to give up, I couldn't go on doing it. It was a nice change, I enjoyed going at Saturday, and Christmastime, yo
u know. And they used to send me home in a taxi up here.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you first started work you continued to live at home, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did starting work change your relationship at all with your parents? Or with your brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, we just kept... we've always kept the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you spend your Sunday any differently, or did you still go on going to Sunday School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I went to Church, yes. I'm afraid when I got to the shop the church got neglected.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you got to Bradford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Yes, 'cos we had to do a lot ... a Sunday, many a time, you see. Although I got a box to put money in from the Church near and the vicar said 'I wish I had 50 like you'. I never knew what I put in, I used to keep dropping stuff, money in this
 box and oh, I got quite a lot in. He said 'I wish I had 50 people like you, all me worries'd be over'. Although I didn't go to church much, I tried to help that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What were your views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, my views are Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Were they then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes. Never been any different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you vote at all in the 1918 election? Do you remember, the first time that women could vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I should do. I can't remember, but I should do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 It didn't make a great impact on you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Have you done anything in political activities at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
No. Me brother-in-law did and my husband used to ... when we were at Bradford he used to bring the car up and help, you know, taking people to vote, and that. That's all we done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
You've already mentioned some of the ways in which you used to spend your spare time when you were getting into your 'teens and starting work, and so on, like your Sunday School class and things of this sort; is the
re anything else that you can remember that you started to do then that you hadn't done before?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, I didn't seem to have any interests only in the Church and Sunday School, that's all. That was me only interest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you go out in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, not a right ... not a lot, but I didn't go out. I didn't go out a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Where would you go to? And who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 I didn't go out a lot in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you make any new friends about this time, boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. When we got to Bradford I made friends at Bradford with some people had a shop in the block that we got very friendly with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But not while you were still at Keighley, when you started to work you didn't make any new friends then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any special friends about that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No. Oh, I had one friend, yes. She's dead, now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What would you do? Where would you go with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, we used to go to each other's house, mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
When they ... you know, we used to go to each other's house. I know I used to go to her house when her mother had been baking, making cake, you know, things like that. You know, simple enjoyment in those days, hadn't you, you didn't need a lot to entertai
n you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No, they never asked us, I think they trusted us. And then, 1917 I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 , I think. Yes, 1917, 'cos he was in khaki and the best man was in hospital blue, his friend. He died not a long time after through some war wounds, I think, the best man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long has you known your husband when you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I'd known the family for a few years but not been friendly with him especially, you know. I'd known one of his
 brothers, better. There were five brothers and I'd known one of his brothers better than him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, I don't know. See, I'd known him ... I don't think it was the ... I helped at the YMCA bazaar in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 caf\'e9}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  but it wasn't then I k
new him. Before then he used to sometimes wait about and go on home with me, you see, if I were out at Sunday night, and that was how I started, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did he come from Keighley?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, from Riddlesden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And he was a painter and decorator then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 When you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Yes. Then he went in the Army and then he started, when he come back he painted the trams in Keighley. He left there to go to the shop, you see, he left for the shop. And he was to teach everything, it was hard work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 To teach the staff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Him. No, he didn't know anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You used to have to teach him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, he didn't know anything. But he got on well with the customers and he was all right, we did very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you save up before you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, I saved ... I don't know, I hadn't a lot, I think about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12135312 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 44. I don't know what he had. 'Cos I think he'd made a Will before we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 when he was in the Army and left what he had to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did your parents help you in setting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Financially, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Financially or in kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 His father came down and helped us putting curtains up at Bradford, but we didn't go to Bradford straight away, but when we went there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you actually establish a home when you first got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 , or was it not until after the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 We was at my home a bit, and then we was at his parents' home a bit before we got to Bradford, waiting to go, you see, to the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How long were you engaged before you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 A few years, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Could you describe the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, it was a War wedding, I didn't get anything new. I had a brown two piece and a brown velvet hat with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9322618\charrsid1930154 an}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  orange coloured flower in, I know, and some lace-up brown boots. That's what I had on, but they weren't new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have any wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes, yes, there would be wedding presents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Was there a reception, did you have guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, we had a ... we went to a caf\'e9, you know, had a meal. There wasn't a big lot there
, 20 or 30, I should think there, that's all. But it was gradually going up. Me sister, she'd got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
 in the September and ours was January and we had the same things and it'd gone up 10/-d. a head.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That was a lot!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, well, it had gone up
 10/-d. a head from then, just those few months, and the catering it was just the same as what she'd had, and the same number of people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 About how many would...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Twenty or 30, I'm not right sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Did you have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He'd only a few days off out of the Army. We went to Starbeck to his aunt's and stayed 'till he went back. We were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  on the Tuesday, I think, and he'd to go back on the Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How old was he when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 He was a year younger than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Did he do any other jobs at all, either before or after, apart from the painting and decorating, and the work on the trams, and the business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You worked in the business, obviously, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Oh, yes. Yes, I did the books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did your husband feel about your working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Oh, he didn't seem to mind. We had somebody to help with the cleaning, you see, to do the cleaning. I had to pay somebody for that because I hadn't the time 'cos I'd other things to do, and I'd rather do the other things than the cleaning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How do you think that your husband felt about his work? You know, any of it. Did he like his work when he was a painter and decorator?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, yes, he did. Yes, he liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And how did he like running the business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, he got to like that, and people all liked him because he was lively and jokey, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And this would be about 1919, would it, when you started in the business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Before you actually were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10055685 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154  did you have to be home by a certain time at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 No later than 10, and you got into trouble if you were, if you were later than 10 o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 And this was while you were courting, was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Yes, yes, all the time. 'Cos it 
... I used to help at ... I didn't work in the shop but I used to help sometimes in one of the retail shops and it was open 'till 11 at night, you see, I was later than, getting home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 But you were working so that would be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 That would be different, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You worked pretty long hours, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
Yes. And for working this Saturday what did you get? From noon 'till that time I think it was two shillings. You could get a lot for two shillings then, couldn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 How did your wage increased over the time you were there? You say you were on this piecework rate to begin with
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
I didn't get a lot when I finished up in the office, I'd only ... and I were doing all this, taking all this money ... twenty-six shillings a week. But they helped me in other ways when we were starting at the shop. I got repaid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10360694 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 You mean they helped you with getting connections, or stock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1599224 SC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 Well, with getting stock. I paid for it, and that, but .... And also with some money just at the time we 
were buying it, you see, which we paid ... I paid them back, straight away, but which wasn't just available then. So I really got repaid for anything I'd done.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid10360694 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7549636\charrsid1930154 
\par }}